'''Shintō Taikyō''' (神道大教), formerly called '''Shinto Honkyoku''' (神道本局), is a [[Japan]]ese [[Shintoism|Shintoist]] organization, and was established by Meiji officials in 1873.<ref>http://www.adherents.com/Na/Na_602.html</ref> It is recognized officially,<ref>http://www.joyofsects.com/world/shinto.shtml</ref> and its headquarters are in [[Tokyo]].<ref>http://eos.kokugakuin.ac.jp/modules/xwords/entry.php?entryID=652</ref> It has many shrines, <ref>http://www.novelguide.com/a/discover/ear_01/ear_01_00184.html</ref> and [[Tenrikyo]] used to be under its jurisdiction.<ref>http://www.tenrikyo.or.jp/en/newsletter/html/tt5/genten_kyoten.html</ref>
